data.description: Welcome to this Key West Coastal inspired home situated on a beautiful one-acre piece of land. This two-story architecture offers an abundance of natural light with a semi-open concept. The first-floor footprint gives way to an inviting foyer with a grand family room equipped with gorgeous sightlines to the rear landscape and deck with cathedral ceilings. The guest bedrooms and bathroom, along with the laundry room are all located on the primary floor. The stunning kitchen is complete with stainless steel  appliances, stone countertops, solid wood cabinets, open shelving, and a quaint island with butcher block top. The dining area sits stoically amidst a stunning picturesque windowscape for an inviting feel. Head upstairs to the second floor where you will be met with an entire primary floor suite. The second story includes an expansive loft with a built-in closet and overlooks the primary floor family area. It also provides french doors that walk out onto a stunning covered balcony. The primary bedroom is vast in size with french doors leading to a comforting balcony that overlooks the rear landscape. The primary bathroom has a stunning walk-in stone tiled shower with multiple shower heads and a large single vanity. The home comes equipped with 26 3x5 solar panels, a tankless water heater, and much more! Come make this tranquil home your own!
